title: The Book of Fine Prints - An Anthology of Printed Pictures and I
description:
Pdf / English / 1948 / 499 pages / 90 MB / 600 ILLUSTRATIONS

by Carl Zigrosser
Curator of Prints, Drawings and lllustrated Books at the Philadelphia Museum of Art

A comprehensive and authoritative and lavishly illustrated work covering the history
of prints and print-making throughout the world, from the first "rubbings" in China
more than ten centuries ago to today's etchings, lithographs, aquatints, woodcuts,
engravings, silk-screen and other prints, including Chinese and Japanese prints.
